<div id="sub-page">
    <h2>BE03 - A company is looking for a supplier in Poland</h2>
<h3>The package is address to:</h3>
<p>Companies interested in winning new suppliers of components, semi-finished products or services in Poland.</p>
<p>Within the framework of this program we offer a package consisting of:</p>
<p><strong>Stage_1 Preparations and Arrangements.<br /></strong>1.1 Establishing Client&rsquo;s detailed needs and expectations.<br />1.2 Preparation of the project&rsquo;s assumptions including: Scope, Requirements, Time and Costs.</p>
<p><strong>Stage_2 Project Commencement &amp; Monitoring.</strong><br />2.1 Team designation and project leader appointment <br />2.2 Project monitoring through: <br />- cyclical reviews of work progress (tele- and video conferences)<br />- project tracking with Gatt/PDCA method or CPM, PERT and other methods in the case of more advanced projects<br />- reporting</p>
<p><strong>Stage_3 Selection of target group.</strong><br />3.1 Selection of potential partners in accordance with established criteria.<br />3.2 SWAT analysis of selected partners.<br />3.3 Initial interviews (without the principals&rsquo; participation).<br />3.4 Preparation of selected partners&rsquo; portfolios /profile. <br />3.5 Presentation of selected group&rsquo;s profiles (market and financial position, verification of reliability, etc.)</p>
<p><strong>Stage_4 Meeting with selected target group.</strong><br />4.1 Organisation of meeting (hotel booking, transportation, interpreter, etc. &ndash; see additional offers).<br />4.2 Animation of the meeting of selected group <br />4.3 Organisation and animation of the &ldquo;face to face&rdquo; meeting with selected candidates.<br />4.4 Visits to selected locations.</p>
<p><strong>Stage_5 After-meeting service.<br /></strong>5.1 Preparation of summarising report.<br />5.2 Coordination of contacts with the meeting&rsquo;s participants.</p>
<p><strong>Stage_6 Finalisation.</strong><br />6.1 Legal and substantive support during finalising final terms and conditions of cooperation with selected partner.<br />6.2 Other according to arrangements with the principal.</p>
<p><strong>Stage_7 Completion of the project.</strong></p>
<p>*) the presented text does not constitute a commercial offer within the meaning of legal regulations</p>
    <p style="font-size: 150%; text-align: right;"><a href="/de/b2b-business-events">Rückseite</a></p>
</div>

